column6: SPIDER-MAN: BIG TIME! Norman Osborn is at the heart of a prison riot! Third Wing is on lockdown as five of the deadliest super-villains in the world wreak havoc...and the only man who can control them is the world's most dangerous psychopath, the Green Goblin! Will Osborn succeed in bending to his will a force of evil with the combined power to destroy the world as we know it? And what happens if they get out?
